column13:
An apparatus (1) for holding a bicycle wheel in a bicycle frame, including: 
an elongate member (3); 
a first engaging member (5) positioned at one end of the elongate member (3); 
a second engaging member (7) positioned at an opposite end of the elongate member (3); and 
a pivotally moveable actuating member (9) for effecting movement of the second engaging member (7) towards the first engaging member (5); 
wherein the actuating member (9) includes holding means (11) for engaging with a spoke of the bicycle wheel.
